        <mxCell id="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-31" value="- Plan an outline.&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;- Decide what, if any, web searches are needed to gather more information.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Write an initial response&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Read over the first response to spot any incorrect information against ground truths and user&#39;s personal preferences&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Revise the draft taking into account any weaknesses spotted.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- And so on.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1">
          <mxGeometry x="360" y="50" width="250" height="130" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-33" value="Key Agent Components" style="swimlane;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1">
          <mxGeometry x="640" y="30" width="200" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-37" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Reflection&lt;/b&gt;: The LLM examines its own work to come up with ways to improve it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Tool use&lt;/b&gt;: The LLM is given tools such as web search (Web Voyager), code execution (API Calls), or any other function to help it gather information, take action, or process data.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Planning:&lt;/b&gt; The LLM comes up with, and executes, a multistep plan to achieve a goal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Multi-agent collaboration&lt;/b&gt;: More than one AI agent work together, splitting up tasks (Data collection, Response generation, response evaluation, sentiment analysis, etc.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-33">
          <mxGeometry y="20" width="200" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
